textAnnotations.description:
WPC campaign against NATO
YES TO PEACE!
NO TO NAT!
Protest NATO's Summit! May 2017 in Brussels!
Tuesday 23rd May from 19.00-22:00
INTAL Public event against NATO,
with the support of the WPC
Meeting Hall "de Spiegelzaal" at De Markten,
Wednesday 24th May 11:00-16:00
WPC Conference against NATO
"Yes to Peace-No to NATO"
Meeting Hall "Sleep Well Hostel"
Rue du Damier 23, 1000 Brussels
Oude Graanmarkt 5, 1000 Brussels
Wednesday 24th May 1700
Anti-NATO Rally of INTAL and other Belgian Organizations
Concentration at 17.00 at Gare du Nord (North Station)
March with the WPC block of members and friends
World Peace Council/www.wpc-in.org
